data.description: Conveniently located 4 bedroom home with fenced yard. New roof October 2023!! Open living room/dining room. Split floor plan with primary bedroom and bath on the left and 3 bedrooms and bath on the right. Great opportunity to get into a 4 bedroom home in a nice community at a reasonable price. 35 min to Mooresville, 20 mins to Statesville, 25 mins to Winston/Salem, 20 mins to Lexington, 25 mins to Salisbury, 45 mins to Charlotte. (Times are approximates)(Roof installed after pictures were taken)
